    <h1><%= title %></h1>
    <br>
    <br>
    <div id="text-part">
      <p>Real time data is sent from various sensors installed within the cattle shed at regular intervals. Measurements are taken 5 times a day and responsive actions are automatically implemented daily to ensure that shed conditions remain at peek.</p>
      <p>To see a daily summary of measurements and complementary actions taken, please click on the button below</p>
      <% if(error) { %>
        <%= error %>
      <% } %>
      <br>
      <br>
      <br>
      <div>
        <form action="/water" method="get">
          <input class="button" type="button" value="Get Water Conditions" onclick="document.getElementById('hidden').style.display = 'block' ;"/>
        </form>
      </div>
      <br>
      <button class="button"><a href="/shed">Check Air Monitoring Page</a></button></a>
    </div>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <div id="hidden">
      <div id="text-part">
        <b>Average Measurements of Today:</b>
        <br>
        <ul>
            <li>Average Water Quality (pH): <%= avgWaterQuality %></li>
            <li>Average Water Quantity (in l): <%= avgWaterQuantity %></li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <br>
        <b>Automatic Actions Taken Today:</b>
        <%= alertMessage %>
      </div>
    </div> 
  </body>
